data.description: Welcome home to 2006 Anderson Farm Rd! This beauty is only 10 mins away from West Florence and 10 mins away from Darlington. With an attractive corner lot sitting at 0.70 acre, you will find a huge fenced in back yard with a wired workshop and outside storage shed. Step inside to find plenty of space in the open floor plan with 2 living areas, dining room and an AHmazing kitchen! Speaking of kitchen, check out the beautiful brick/stone stove surrounding. Plenty of cabinets and counterspace! Kitchen flooring was just updated. Walk over to the family room and take a seat on the leather sectional sleeper sofa, which stays! Dine on the beautiful round kitchen table, which also stays! Got laundry? Well this laundry room is sure to please because it is huge! The bedrooms are a split floor plan. Master has new carpet, walk in closet, and a very spacious master bath. Soak in the garden tub or take a quick shower. Did i mention the New roof Oct 2023, New furnace Oct 2023, New back steps Oct 2023? So what are you waiting for? Schedule your tour today! Seller will sell as-is.
